The Flory-Huggins parameter (χ) reflecting the miscibility of the donor-acceptor predicts the phase separation in the BHJ layer61. In Supplementary Fig. 29 and Supplementary Table 14, the parameter of χ was calculated by the equation described as χ = K(γD−γA)2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
